auto_correlation

Auto correlation of finite discrete sequence

Calling Sequence

[Rxx] = auto_correlation(x)

Parameters

x: input discrete sequence
Rxx: auto-correlation output sequence

Description

auto_correlation -Auto correlation of a discrete sequence

Examples

x = [1,2,3,4,5];//input sequence
[Rxx] = auto_correlation(x);
L = length(Rxx);
M = floor(L/2);
plot2d3('gnn',[-M:M],Rxx)
title('Auto Correlation Sequence')

